event: The mouse pointer is clicking on the "CDROM (D:)" icon.
description: The user clicked the "CDROM (D:)" icon within the "My Computer" window. As a result, the drive information displayed in the window's right pane was updated.
outcome: The contents of the "My Computer" window's right pane have been updated, displaying "CDROM (D:)" drive information.

event: The mouse is clicking on the close button of the window titled "CDROM (D:)".
description: The user clicks the close button of the "CDROM (D:)" window. As a result, the window closes.
outcome: The "CDROM (D:)" window is no longer visible.

event: The mouse is clicking on the "Free AOL & Unlimited..." desktop shortcut.
description: The user clicks the "Free AOL & Unlimited..." shortcut on the desktop.  As a result, the "Creating a New Profile" window appears.
outcome: A new window titled "Creating a New Profile" appeared over the desktop. The window contains text describing the purpose of user profiles, and buttons for "Back", "Next", "Finish", and "Cancel". The "Next" button is highlighted.

event: The key following key(s) were pressed: ['Shift_L', 'B'].
description: The user pressed the keyboard shortcut 'Shift + B', equivalent to clicking the **< Back** button in the "Enter your Name and Email Address" dialog box.
outcome: The "Enter your Name and Email Address" dialog box closed and the "Creating a New Profile" dialog box is visible.

event: The key following key(s) were pressed: ['o'].
description: The user typed the letter "o" into the "Full Name" field.

event: The key following key(s) were pressed: ['b'].
description: The user pressed the 'b' key. No visual changes occurred as a result of this event.

event: The key following key(s) were pressed: ['space'].
description: The user pressed the 'space' key. No observable changes occurred in the "Enter Your Name and Email Address" dialog box.

event: The key following key(s) were pressed: ['Shift_L', 'A'].
description: The user pressed the keyboard shortcut "Shift + A" while focused on the "Enter your Name and Email Address" dialog box. No observable changes occurred in the user interface.

event: The key following key(s) were pressed: ['l', 'i'].
description: The user typed the first two characters, "li",  into the "Full Name" text field.

event: The key following key(s) were pressed: ['c'].
description: The user pressed the 'c' key. No visible changes occurred in the GUI.

event: The key following key(s) were pressed: ['e'].
description: The user typed the letter "e" into the "Full Name" text field within the "Enter your Name and Email Address" dialog box.

event: The key following key(s) were pressed: ['s'].
description: The user typed the letter "s" into the "Full Name" text field within the "Enter your Name and Email Address" dialog box.

event: The key following key(s) were pressed: ['o'].
description: The user typed the letter "o" into the "Full Name" field.

event: The key following key(s) were pressed: ['n'].
description: The user pressed the 'n' key, which triggered the "Next >" button in the "Enter your Name and Email Address" dialog box. As a result, the dialog box closed, and the "Choose a Name and Directory for your Profile" dialog box appeared.
outcome: The "Enter your Name and Email Address" dialog box is no longer present, and the "Choose a Name and Directory for your Profile" dialog box has appeared.
